text.section:
This section does not prohibit:
A retailer that is in possession of a product prohibited for manufacture, lease, sale, or distribution for sale or lease under subsections (b) and (c) of this section from selling, recycling, or otherwise disposing of a product that is in the retailer's or lessor's inventory on or after the date that the prohibition takes effect;
A person from recycling a product that contains decaBDE;
A person from selling, leasing, recycling, or otherwise disposing of a product that contains recycled decaBDE;
Any activity involving a product that contains decaBDE that occurs subsequent to first sale at retail; or
A person from transporting or storing a product prohibited under subsections (b) and (c) of this section for later distribution outside the State.
